{"tid":1960534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共 : 供應短缺下已不能保證公屋上樓時間 正籌備於明年年中發放租金津貼","createTime":"2020-04-06T08:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T06:16:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"95ee24fede80f5742e3a1ef22a258300c2555be6","tid":1960534,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"陳帆：代繳租金措施可在撥款通過一個月至個半月後實施<br />\n06.04.2020 16:10<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局長陳帆在立法會特別財委會表示，欠缺土地供應之下，政府在房屋供應正在追落後，他沒有水晶球可以確保劏房戶要等多久可以上樓，但政府會盡力而為。他又表示，香港前景面臨挑戰，經濟下行是不爭的事實，房委會和房協為低收入租戶代繳一個月租金的措施，可以在撥款通過一個月至個半月後實施，政府亦正籌備向輪候公屋超過3年的合資格住戶提供津貼，期望明年年中推出。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆又指，立法會議事進程有相當大的延誤，一手樓空置稅的人手安排仍未開始籌備，他會靜觀其變，再作適當部署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279045&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279045%26csid%3D261_341&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=5ee1e9e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279045&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a51585f0bedc3c953d04a63695096a5bd1ae2ef5","tid":1960534,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"有樓又贏"},{"pid":"1a37a22ad37597ea255c006dc2d10054f45b711e","tid":1960534,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"業主又有得加租"},{"pid":"aecf0d249105992671bb4eb874d550160c7b75e1","tid":1960534,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:35:28.000Z","msg":"俾撚曬班豬西隔離"},{"pid":"d19e87a4534224a8f5f4aa134b89fdca4b8f8ada","tid":1960534,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:36:38.000Z","msg":"係做野就租金管制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bec0d479a87d66370842264dbeddcfb91850afb","tid":1960534,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0